(2348, 8, 'Solar SpeedRack SpeedFoot Kit Black', '', '<p>Solar SpeedRack SpeedFoot Kit Black</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Part Number:&nbsp;SA-ASM-SQF01-BC</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-Pentrating Mount Attachment</li>\r\n	<li>Reduces roof penetrations</li>\r\n	<li>Made from recycled materials</li>\r\n	<li>Comes pre-assmbled</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The Solar SpeedFoot is an&nbsp;innovative weight distribution block made of recycled materials and comes with an aluminum L-Foot. Install this mount between penetrations with a 5/16&quot; T-Bolt or fastener with a 1/2&quot; Drive Socket. The Solar SpeedFoot provides additional support to distribute dead load across the interior span of the rail between penetrations. The L-Foot can be flipped for a higher adjustable range and clearance.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>Limited Warranty Conditions</strong><br />\r\nSeller warrants that the Products, when delivered by Seller and for twenty (20) years following the delivery&nbsp;date (the &ldquo;Warranty Period&rdquo;), will be free from defects in material and workmanship, except that any factoryapplied&nbsp;anodized finish is warranted to be free from substantial manufacturing related visible peeling or&nbsp;cracking<br />\r\nor chalking under normal atmospheric conditions for a period of five (5) years (&ldquo;Finish Warranty&rdquo;)&nbsp;and&nbsp;will substantially conform to Seller&#39;s publicly available specifications for such Products in effect at the&nbsp;time&nbsp;of delivery. In the event that the product does not conform to this warranty during the Warranty Period,&nbsp;Solar&nbsp;SpeedRack&reg; will, at its option, either repair or replace the product or pay the cost of having the&nbsp;product&nbsp;repaired or replaced. To the extent permitted by law, Solar SpeedRack&rsquo;s total liability under this&nbsp;warranty&nbsp;will in no circumstances exceed the repair or replacement of the product or payment of the cost of<br />\r\nhaving&nbsp;the product repaired or replaced. In the event of re